# SODAPOP 2.0 Coding Rules
- Framework: Vanilla JS / HTML5 / CSS3 (Jamstack)
- UI Principle: Google Antigravity (Floating cards, Glassmorphism, Smooth transitions)
- Data Logic: Always filter out "ê³„" (Total) from KOSIS API results.
- Code Style: Use Modern ES6+, Utility-first CSS patterns.
- Administrative Logic: Follow the 10-digit H-Code mapping (Sido-Sigungu-EMD).